# Rust build output + Tauri codegen
/target/
/gen/schemas/
# LAN bench server assets staged by the vite desktop profile
# (fs-stage-shadercarousel-desktop). The tracked .gitkeep keeps the dir
# present on fresh checkouts: tauri-build resolves bundle.resources on EVERY
# cargo build/check/test, and a missing dir fails the build script before
# anything compiles (an empty dir is skipped gracefully).
/carousel-dist/*
!/carousel-dist/.gitkeep
